**  History:
**
**	11-oct-95 (fraser)
**	    DBI change.  Added code to create tables for OpenIngres/Desktop.
**	    Removed commit statements which are unnecessary because this
**	    procedure is now run in autocommit mode.
**	12-oct-95 (fraser)
**	    Changed customer_id to integer not null.
**	14-oct-95 (fraser)
**	    DBI change.  Changed insert statements that were inserting an
**	    empty string into a not-nullable varchar variable.  Both IOD and
**	    Oracle treat an empty string as a null.  Insert ' ' rather than ''.
**	19-oct-95 (judyv)
