**	    procedures around for a while, in case we get overruled.)
**	24-nov-97 (dansa02)
**	    The Videos demo actually contains an example frame (TableUpdate)
**	    that uses a subset of the "part" table from the old Customer_Order
**	    demo.  We're not shipping Customer_Order anymore, so "part" is not
**	    normally available.  Instead, I've added a new "partsample" (just
**	    the subset of "part" used by TableUpdate) to the Videos table list.
